alerts.title: Flood Watch for Mason, WA
alerts.description:
...FLOOD WATCH REMAINS IN EFFECT THROUGH LATE FRIDAY NIGHT...
THE FLOOD WATCH CONTINUES FOR
* A PORTION OF NORTHWEST WASHINGTON...INCLUDING THE FOLLOWING
COUNTY...MASON.
* THROUGH LATE FRIDAY NIGHT
* A STRONG WARM FRONT WILL BRING HEAVY RAIN TO THE OLYMPICS
TONIGHT THROUGH THURSDAY NIGHT. THE HEAVY RAIN WILL PUSH THE
SKOKOMISH RIVER ABOVE FLOOD STAGE TODAY...AND MAJOR FLOODING IS
POSSIBLE.
* A FLOOD WARNING IS IN EFFECT FOR THE SKOKOMISH RIVER. THE FLOOD
WATCH REMAINS IN EFFECT FOR MASON COUNTY FOR THE POSSIBILITY OF
AREAL FLOODING ASSOCIATED WITH A MAJOR FLOOD.
